snippet.title: Nintendo DS Longplay [116] Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 3: Mutant Nightmare
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: NPI

This is a long one although it shouldn't supposed to be but I wanted to go for 100%

Each turtle has different abilities and their storylines are a bit different. I collected all of the crystals and unlocked all pictures in the gallery. This is the time stamp for how I managed to get everything, but you can chose to play different paths if you want. There is also a lot of repeated levels and bosses.

The main playthrough is up until the world 4 and level 1 (including this first level).

00:00:38 Leonardo's playthrough
01:13:00 Raphael's playthrough
02:22:59 Donatelo's playthrough
03:37:31 Michelangelo's playthrough

Then you have to repeat the world 4 bosses levels to get to the final boss and see the ending, which is in different order for each one of the main selected turtle.

04:56:46 World 4 boss levels of all the other turtles again
05:10:08 Final Boss with Michelangelo
05:12:03 Michelangelo's ending

05:15:39 World 4 boss levels of all the other turtles again
05:26:55 Final Boss with Leonardo
05:28:29 Leonardo's ending

05:32:00 World 4 boss levels of all the other turtles again
05:44:53 Final Boss with Raphael
05:46:25 Raphael's ending

05:49:55 World 4 boss levels of all the other turtles again
06:01:53 Final Boss with Donatelo
06:04:00 Donatelo's ending

06:07:17 Gallery -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
